Dawood Ibrahim -LRB- Marathi : दाऊद इब्राहीम कासकर , born Dawood Ibrahim Kaskar 26 December 1955 -RRB- , known as Dawood Bhai or simply Bhai is a gangster and terrorist originally from Dongri in Mumbai , India .
The word `` Bhai '' means `` Big brother '' .
In the lingo of the Mumbai underworld , the word `` Bhai '' is attributed to members of the underworld who hold considerable power .
He heads the Indian organised crime syndicate D-Company founded in Mumbai .
He is currently on the wanted list of Interpol for cheating , criminal conspiracy and running an organised crime syndicate .
He was number three on the The World 's 10 Most Wanted .